 {
  "text": "Hi Zilaudio, this is David from Continental Grain in Chicago. I just sent you an e-mail, so this is only a quick message. In the e-mail, I attached a short form. I asked for two things: your total tons and your final price. Please read the e-mail and reply to me by Friday, because our schedule this month is very tight. After you send the form, I will call you to confirm everything. Thank you, and talk to you soon.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a4_listening_david.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Good morning, and here is a short reminder about your week. You have two deadlines. The first one is the soybean form for Continental Grain. Please send it before Friday. The second one is the price confirmation for the meeting on Monday. Remember to check every attachment before you reply, and confirm the dates in your schedule. If you send the documents early, you have more time before the weekend. Have a good week.",
